- change_start: Change the bot start character spaces also count(this will be case sensitive)
- hello: Reply hello with the user"s name
- logs: Set the logs channel to be sent the logs
- lock: Toggling locking the bot to be only used in the default channel or server-wide
- long_reference: Enable long reference, reply any message with the word "long" with long reference image
- encrypt/decrypt: Encrypt/decrypt your message with a special encryption type(be fast, the message will be deleted after 5 seconds)
